---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="ABOUT"
  description="关于 PhSeCl 的简介、兴趣方向与正在延展的个人轨迹。"
  titleKey="page.about"
  titleFallback="ABOUT"
  seoTitleKey="seo.about.title"
  seoDescriptionKey="seo.about.description"
  seoTitleFallback="ABOUT"
  seoDescriptionFallback="关于 PhSeCl 的简介、兴趣方向与正在延展的个人轨迹。"
>
  <section class="about-intro">
    <div class="avatar-shell">
      <div class="avatar-fallback" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <img
        src="/media/people/avatar.webp"
        alt="PhSeCl avatar"
        class="avatar"
        onerror="this.classList.add('is-hidden')"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="intro-copy">
      <p data-i18n="about.intro">
        在这里，我想把技术、日常、审美和那些深夜里短暂却真实的想法，慢慢整理成可以回看的文字。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2 data-i18n="about.skills">兴趣 / Skills</h2>
    <div class="tag-list">
      <span>TypeScript</span>
      <span>Astro</span>
      <span>Canvas</span>
      <span>日本語</span>
      <span>音楽</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2 data-i18n="about.timeline">歩いてきた道</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">2025</div>
        <div class="content">
          <h3>PhSeCl Blog Rebuild</h3>
          <p>用 Astro 重构个人站，整理写作、作品和长期维护的结构基础。</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">2024</div>
        <div class="content">
          <h3>Creative Frontend Experiments</h3>
          <p>开始更系统地探索 Canvas、动效表达和偏氛围化的网页叙事。</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">Future</div>
        <div class="content">
          <h3>More notes, more works</h3>
          <p><!-- 后续将在这里扩展更完整的时间线内容 --></p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .avatar-shell {
    position: relative;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
  }

  .avatar-fallback,
  .avatar {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .avatar-fallback {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(245, 184, 204, 0.8), rgba(122, 46, 74, 0.65));
  }

  .avatar {
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid rgba(220, 160, 190, 0.16);
  }

  .avatar.is-hidden {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .intro-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(224, 198, 210, 0.78);
    line-height: 1.95;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: var(--sakura-100);
    font-family: 'Zen Old Mincho', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .tag-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }

  .tag-list span {
    border: 1px solid rgba(160, 60, 100, 0.2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 0.28em 0.9em;
    color: var(--sakura-300);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.35rem;
    top: 0.3rem;
    bottom: 0.3rem;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(220, 160, 190, 0.25), transparent);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5rem minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.2rem;
    top: 0.35rem;
    width: 0.55rem;
    height: 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--sakura-400);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(212, 120, 154, 0.25);
  }

  .timeline .year {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .timeline .content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
    color: var(--sakura-100);
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .timeline .content p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(210, 180, 194, 0.68);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-intro {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .avatar-shell {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }
  }
</style>
